Right low, lunge right.</font>

11
00:02:23,248 --> 00:02:25,949
<font color="#FFFFFF">你要是弄坏什么东西, 修女会要了我的命.
You break anything, the Septa will have my head.</font>

12
00:02:25,984 --> 00:02:27,784
<font color="#FFFFFF">怎么...
- What is— -</font>

13
00:02:38,861 --> 00:02:41,629
<font color="#FFFFFF">你妹妹很清楚我们今天要走.
Your sister knew perfectly well we were to leave today.</font>

14
00:02:41,663 --> 00:02:43,831
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 她怎么会忘记... - 她没有忘记.
- How she could forget— - She didn't forget.</font>

15
00:02:43,865 --> 00:02:46,567
<font color="#FFFFFF">她跟她的舞蹈老师在一起. 每天早上都是.
She's with her dancing master. She's with him every morning.</font>

16
00:02:46,602 --> 00:02:49,138
<font color="#FFFFFF">她总是带着满身瘀伤回来. 她真是笨手笨脚.
She always comes back with scrapes and bruises. She's so clumsy.</font>

17
00:02:49,171 --> 00:02:51,073
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>别出声!
— Hush!</i></font>

18
00:02:51,108 --> 00:02:53,308
<font color="#FFFFFF">回你的房间去.
Go back to your room.</font>

19
00:02:54,243 --> 00:02:55,646
<font color="#FFFFFF">插上门闩
Bar the doors</font>

20
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,881
<font color="#FFFFFF">绝不要给不认识的人开门.
and do not open them for anyone you do not know.</font>

21
00:02:57,915 --> 00:03:00,584
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 怎么了? 出什么事了? - 照我说的做.
- What is it? What's happening? - Do as I told you.</font>

22
00:03:00,618 --> 00:03:02,419
<font color="#FFFFFF">快跑!
Run!</font>

23
00:03:06,157 --> 00:03:07,824
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>这边!
This way!</i></font>

24
00:03:21,336 --> 00:03:23,504
<font color="#FFFFFF">左, 右. 右!
Left, right. Rah!</font>

25
00:03:23,538 --> 00:03:25,240
<font color="#FFFFFF">现在你死了.
Now you are dead.</font>

26
00:03:25,274 --> 00:03:27,241
<font color="#FFFFFF">你说的是右边,
You said right,</font>

27
00:03:27,276 --> 00:03:29,144
<font color="#FFFFFF">但你打的却是左边.
but you went left.</font>

28
00:03:29,177 --> 00:03:31,378
<font color="#FFFFFF">结果你是个死女孩了.
And now you are a dead girl.</font>

29
00:03:31,413 --> 00:03:33,014
<font color="#FFFFFF">可是你骗人了.
Only 'cause you lied.</font>

30
00:03:33,049 --> 00:03:35,682
<font color="#FFFFFF">我的舌头骗人了. 可我的眼睛...
My tongue lied. My eyes</font>

31
00:03:35,716 --> 00:03:38,920
<font color="#FFFFFF">说的是真话. 只是你没看见.
shouted the truth. You were not seeing.</font>

32
00:03:38,954 --> 00:03:41,456
<font color="#FFFFFF">我明明看了, 但你...
I was so. I watched, but you—</font>

33
00:03:41,490 --> 00:03:44,960
<font color="#FFFFFF">看了不等于看见了, 死女孩.
watching is not seeing, dead girl.</font>

34
00:03:47,030 --> 00:03:50,665
<font color="#FFFFFF">只有看见, 只有真正的洞察,
The seeing, the true seeing,</font>

35
00:03:50,699 --> 00:03:53,135
<font color="#FFFFFF">才是剑术的精髓.
that is the heart of swordplay.</font>

36
00:03:57,641 --> 00:04:00,144
<font color="#FFFFFF">艾莉亚史塔克, 跟我们走.
Arya Stark, come with us.</font>

37
00:04:00,177 --> 00:04:02,913
<font color="#FFFFFF">你父亲要见你.
Your father wants to see you.</font>

38
00:04:02,948 --> 00:04:05,316
<font color="#FFFFFF">可是为什么...
And why is it</font>

39
00:04:05,349 --> 00:04:07,784
<font color="#FFFFFF">艾德大人会派兰尼斯特家的人...
that Lord Eddard is sending Lannister men</font>

40
00:04:07,818 --> 00:04:10,021
<font color="#FFFFFF">而不是他自己的手下来呢? 我很好奇.
in place of his own? I am wondering.</font>

41
00:04:10,055 --> 00:04:13,123
<font color="#FFFFFF">别不识好歹, 舞蹈老师.
Mind your place, dancing master.</font>

42
00:04:13,157 --> 00:04:15,693
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>此事与你无关.
This is no concern of yours.</i></font>

43
00:04:15,727 --> 00:04:17,562
<font color="#FFFFFF">我父亲才不会派你们来呢.
My father wouldn't send you.</font>

44
00:04:21,100 --> 00:04:23,800
<font color="#FFFFFF">而且我也不想跟你们走.
And I don't have to go with you if I don't want.</font>

45
00:04:23,834 --> 00:04:26,170
<font color="#FFFFFF">抓住她.
Take her.</font>

46
00:04:26,204 --> 00:04:30,173
<font color="#FFFFFF">你们是人还是蛇, 居然威胁一个小孩子?
Are you men or snakes, that you would threaten a child?</font>

47
00:04:30,207 --> 00:04:32,343
<font color="#FFFFFF">给我滚开, 矮家伙.
Get out of my way, little man.</font>

48
00:04:32,377 --> 00:04:35,846
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>我是西利欧佛瑞尔...
I am Syrio Forel...</i></font>

49
00:04:35,879 --> 00:04:37,880
<font color="#FFFFFF">外国杂种.
Foreign bastard.</font>

50
00:04:40,617 --> 00:04:44,321
<font color="#FFFFFF">你跟我讲话要放尊重点.
And you will be speaking to me with more respect.</font>

51
00:04:44,355 --> 00:04:46,956
<font color="#FFFFFF">宰了这布拉佛斯人, 把那女孩抓来.
Kill the Braavosi. Bring the girl.</font>

52
00:04:48,494 --> 00:04:51,228
<font color="#FFFFFF">小艾莉亚, 今天我们的舞蹈课至此为止.
Arya child, we are done with dancing for the day.</font>

53
00:04:51,262 --> 00:04:53,898
<font color="#FFFFFF">跑去找你父亲吧.
Run to your father.</font>

54
00:05:14,387 --> 00:05:17,122
<font color="#FFFFFF">该死的东西.
- Bloody oafs. -</font>

55
00:05:17,156 --> 00:05:19,024
<font color="#FFFFFF">快走, 艾莉亚.
Be gone now, Arya.</font>

56
00:05:19,059 --> 00:05:21,627
<font color="#FFFFFF">跟我一起走. 快跑.
Come with me. Run.</font>

57
00:05:23,264 --> 00:05:26,266
<font color="#FFFFFF">布拉佛斯的首席剑士从不临阵脱逃.
The first sword of Braavos does not run.</font>

58
00:05:38,411 --> 00:05:40,312
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>记不记得我们应该</i></font>

59
00:05:38,411 --> 00:05:40,312
<font color="#FFFFFF">What do we say</font>

60
00:05:40,348 --> 00:05:42,281
<font color="#FFFFFF">怎么对死神说话?
to the God of death?</font>

61
00:05:42,316 --> 00:05:44,183
<font color="#FFFFFF">"今天不行."
Not today.</font>

62
00:05:45,718 --> 00:05:47,153
<font color="#FFFFFF">快走.
Go.</font>

63
00:06:12,711 --> 00:06:14,812
<font color="#FFFFFF">今天不行. 今天不行.
Not today. Not today.</font>

64
00:06:24,356 --> 00:06:26,158
<font color="#FFFFFF">你不要过来.
Stay away from me.</font>

65
00:06:26,192 --> 00:06:27,858
<font color="#FFFFFF">我要告诉我父亲.
I'll tell my father.</font>

66
00:06:27,894 --> 00:06:30,862
<font color="#FFFFFF">我要... 我要告诉王后.
I'll— I'll tell the Queen.</font>

67
00:06:30,896 --> 00:06:34,598
<font color="#FFFFFF">你以为是谁派我来的?
Who do you think sent me?</font>

68
00:06:47,112 --> 00:06:48,980
<font color="#FFFFFF">缝衣针.
Needle.</font>

69
00:06:52,218 --> 00:06:54,252
<font color="#FFFFFF">原来她在这儿.
There she is.</font>

70
00:06:54,286 --> 00:06:56,553
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 你想要什么? - 我要抓你, 小狼女.
- What do you want? - I want you, wolf girl.</font>

71
00:06:56,588 --> 00:06:58,290
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 过来. - 不要过来.
- Come here. - Leave me be.</font>

72
00:06:58,324 --> 00:07:00,391
<font color="#FFFFFF">我父亲是首相. 他会奖赏你的.
My father's a lord. He'll reward you.</font>

73
00:07:00,425 --> 00:07:01,992
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>会奖赏我的是王后!
She'll reward me— the Queen!</i></font>

74
00:07:02,026 --> 00:07:04,194
<font color="#FFFFFF">走开!
- Stay away! -</font>

75
00:07:33,293 --> 00:07:36,928
<font color="#FFFFFF">史塔克大人, 你一定渴了.
Lord Stark, you must be thirsty.</font>

76
00:07:38,365 --> 00:07:40,533
<font color="#FFFFFF">瓦里斯.
Varys.</font>

77
00:07:42,336 --> 00:07:44,637
<font color="#FFFFFF">我向你保证里面没有下毒.
I promise you it isn't poisoned.</font>

78
00:07:46,307 --> 00:07:48,608
<font color="#FFFFFF">为什么没人肯信任太监呢?
Why is it no one ever trusts the eunuch?</font>

79
00:07:57,151 --> 00:07:58,920
<font color="#FFFFFF">不太多, 大人.
Not so much, My Lord.</font>

80
00:07:58,954 --> 00:08:00,988
<font color="#FFFFFF">如果我是你的话, 我会留下一点.
I would save the rest, if I were you.</font>

81
00:08:01,023 --> 00:08:04,892
<font color="#FFFFFF">藏好它. 在这地牢里常有人被渴死.
Hide it. Men have been known to die of thirst in these cells.</font>

82
00:08:06,762 --> 00:08:09,264
<font color="#FFFFFF">我的女儿们怎么样了?
What about my daughters?</font>

83
00:08:09,298 --> 00:08:11,834
<font color="#FFFFFF">小的那个看来已经逃出了红堡.
The younger one seems to have escaped the castle.</font>

84
00:08:11,869 --> 00:08:14,069
<font color="#FFFFFF">连我的小小鸟们都找不到她.
Even my little birds cannot find her.</font>

85
00:08:14,103 --> 00:08:17,639
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 珊莎呢? - 依然是乔佛里的未婚妻.
- And Sansa? - Still engaged to Joffrey.</font>

86
00:08:17,673 --> 00:08:21,244
<font color="#FFFFFF">瑟曦会把她留在身边. 但你家其他的人...
Cersei will keep her close. The rest of your household though—</font>

87
00:08:21,278 --> 00:08:23,446
<font color="#FFFFFF">全死了, 我感到很痛心.
all dead, it grieves me to say.</font>

88
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:25,747
<font color="#FFFFFF">我讨厌看到流血.
I do so hate the sight of blood.</font>

89
00:08:27,250 --> 00:08:30,119
<font color="#FFFFFF">我的手下被屠杀时你却袖手旁观.
You watched my men being slaughtered and did nothing.</font>

90
00:08:30,153 --> 00:08:32,455
<font color="#FFFFFF">我只能那样, 大人.
And would again, My Lord.</font>

91
00:08:32,489 --> 00:08:36,892
<font color="#FFFFFF">我既没武器, 又没盔甲, 还被兰尼斯特的武士团团围住.
I was unarmed, unarmored and surrounded by Lannister swords.</font>

92
00:08:36,927 --> 00:08:39,260
<font color="#FFFFFF">你看我象个大英雄吗?
When you look at me do you see a hero?</font>

93
00:08:45,201 --> 00:08:47,568
<font color="#FFFFFF">究竟是什么疯狂念头让你去告诉王后...
What madness led you to tell the Queen</font>

94
00:08:47,604 --> 00:08:50,405
<font color="#FFFFFF">说你知道乔佛里的真实身世?
you had learned the truth about Joffrey's birth?</font>

95
00:08:52,775 --> 00:08:54,743
<font color="#FFFFFF">仁慈的疯狂念头.
The madness of mercy.</font>

96
00:08:56,446 --> 00:08:59,181
<font color="#FFFFFF">希望她能保住她孩子们的性命.
That she might save her children.</font>

97
00:08:59,216 --> 00:09:01,048
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>啊, 孩子们.
Ah, the children.</i></font>

98
00:09:01,083 --> 00:09:03,952
<font color="#FFFFFF">受苦的总是那些无辜者.
It is always the innocents who suffer.</font>

99
00:09:03,986 --> 00:09:06,888
<font color="#FFFFFF">杀死国王的不是那袋酒, 也不是那只野猪.
It wasn't the wine that killed Robert, nor the boar.</font>

100
00:09:06,923 --> 00:09:10,392
<font color="#FFFFFF">酒令他反应迟缓, 野猪撕开了他的肚子,
The wine slowed him down and the boar ripped him open,</font>

101
00:09:10,426 --> 00:09:13,660
<font color="#FFFFFF">但是真正杀死国王的却是你的仁慈.
but it was your mercy that killed the King.</font>

102
00:09:17,231 --> 00:09:20,600
<font color="#FFFFFF">我想你知道自己在劫难逃吧, 艾德大人?
I trust you know you are a dead man, Lord Eddard?</font>

103
00:09:25,338 --> 00:09:27,907
<font color="#FFFFFF">王后不会杀我.
The Queen can't kill me.</font>

104
00:09:27,942 --> 00:09:30,409
<font color="#FFFFFF">凯特还抓着她的弟弟.
Cat holds her brother.</font>

105
00:09:30,445 --> 00:09:33,145
<font color="#FFFFFF">可惜不是她爱的那个弟弟.
The wrong brother sadly.</font>

106
00:09:33,181 --> 00:09:34,914
<font color="#FFFFFF">而且这会儿也跑了.
And lost to her.</font>

107
00:09:34,948 --> 00:09:37,884
<font color="#FFFFFF">你夫人让小恶魔从她的指缝里钻了出去.
Your wife has let the Imp slip through her fingers.</font>

108
00:09:41,722 --> 00:09:44,158
<font color="#FFFFFF">倘若真是这样,
If that's true,</font>

109
00:09:44,192 --> 00:09:47,727
<font color="#FFFFFF">那快快割了我的喉咙, 做个了结.
then slit my throat and be done with it.</font>

110
00:09:47,761 --> 00:09:50,331
<font color="#FFFFFF">今天不会, 大人.
Not today, My Lord.</font>

111
00:09:53,369 --> 00:09:56,203
<font color="#FFFFFF">告诉我, 瓦里斯.
Tell me something, Varys.</font>

112
00:09:56,239 --> 00:09:58,740
<font color="#FFFFFF">你究竟是为谁服务?
Who do you truly serve?</font>

113
00:09:59,976 --> 00:10:02,644
<font color="#FFFFFF">为了国家, 大人.
The Realm, My Lord.</font>

114
00:10:02,679 --> 00:10:04,947
<font color="#FFFFFF">总得有人为国家服务.
Someone must.</font>

115
00:10:23,932 --> 00:10:26,668
<font color="#FFFFFF">这是奥瑟, 肯定没错.
It's Othor, without a doubt.</font>

116
00:10:28,004 --> 00:10:29,604
<font color="#FFFFFF">另外那个是杰佛佛花, 大人,
The other one is Jafer Flowers, My Lord,</font>

117
00:10:29,639 --> 00:10:32,407
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>他的一只手被狼咬掉了.
less the hand the wolf tore off.</i></font>

118
00:10:32,442 --> 00:10:35,443
<font color="#FFFFFF">有班扬或他手下其他人的踪迹吗?
Any sign of Benjen or the rest of his party?</font>

119
00:10:35,479 --> 00:10:38,346
<font color="#FFFFFF">只有这两个, 大人.
Just these two, My Lord.</font>

120
00:10:38,381 --> 00:10:40,383
<font color="#FFFFFF">我看他们死了有一阵子了.
Been dead awhile, I'd say.</font>

121
00:10:40,418 --> 00:10:43,153
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 嗯. - 可是气味...
- Mmm. - The smell.</font>

122
00:10:46,558 --> 00:10:48,158
<font color="#FFFFFF">怎么气味?
What smell?</font>

123
00:10:48,192 --> 00:10:51,229
<font color="#FFFFFF">没有气味.
There is none.</font>

124
00:10:51,263 --> 00:10:54,999
<font color="#FFFFFF">如果他们死了很久, 怎么还没腐烂?
If they'd be dead for a long time, wouldn't there be rot?</font>

125
00:10:55,033 --> 00:10:57,735
<font color="#FFFFFF">我们烧了他们吧.
We should burn them.</font>

126
00:10:57,769 --> 00:11:00,804
<font color="#FFFFFF">雪诺说得没错, 大人. 烧掉尸体吧.
Snow's not wrong, My Lord. Fire will do for them.</font>

127
00:11:00,839 --> 00:11:03,006
<font color="#FFFFFF">野人的处理方式.
The Wildling way.</font>

128
00:11:03,042 --> 00:11:05,777
<font color="#FFFFFF">我要先让伊蒙师傅检查一下这些尸体.
I want Maester Aemon to examine them first.</font>

129
00:11:05,811 --> 00:11:08,980
<font color="#FFFFFF">你也许是个懦夫, 塔利,
You may be a coward, Tarly,</font>

130
00:11:09,014 --> 00:11:11,149
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>但人倒是不笨.
but you're not stupid.</i></font>

131
00:11:11,182 --> 00:11:15,219
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 把他们弄进去. - 照他说的做.
- Get them inside. - You heard him.</font>

132
00:11:16,754 --> 00:11:18,722
<font color="#FFFFFF">总司令,
Lord Commander,</font>

133
00:11:18,756 --> 00:11:21,259
<font color="#FFFFFF">伊蒙师傅正在等你过去...
Maester Aemon awaits you in his chambers—</font>

134
00:11:21,293 --> 00:11:25,129
<font color="#FFFFFF">君临城来了一只渡鸦.
a raven from King's Landing.</font>

135
00:11:25,163 --> 00:11:27,030
<font color="#FFFFFF">快移出去.
Come on, move 'em out.</font>

136
00:11:38,741 --> 00:11:41,609
<font color="#FFFFFF">给我倒杯酒, 雪诺,
Bring me a horn of ale, Snow,</font>

137
00:11:41,644 --> 00:11:44,578
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>再给你自己也倒一杯.
and pour one for yourself.</i></font>

138
00:11:54,389 --> 00:11:56,957
<font color="#FFFFFF">国王死了.
The King is dead.</font>

139
00:12:09,070 --> 00:12:11,604
<font color="#FFFFFF">我父亲有什么消息?
Is there any word of my father?</font>

140
00:12:11,638 --> 00:12:13,873
<font color="#FFFFFF">坐下.
Sit.</font>

141
00:12:18,378 --> 00:12:20,912
<font color="#FFFFFF">史塔克大人...
Lord Stark has been</font>

142
00:12:20,946 --> 00:12:23,548
<font color="#FFFFFF">被控叛国.
charged with treason.</font>

143
00:12:23,581 --> 00:12:25,984
<font color="#FFFFFF">他们说他与劳勃的弟弟共谋
They say he conspired with Robert's brothers</font>

144
00:12:26,018 --> 00:12:28,754
<font color="#FFFFFF">阻止乔佛里王子继位.
to deny the throne to Prince Joffrey.</font>

145
00:12:41,102 --> 00:12:44,740
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>我希望你别打算做任何傻事.
I hope you're not thinking of doing anything stupid.</i></font>

