00:21:33,775 --> 00:21:35,375
<font color="#FFFFFF">石鸦部落的人呢?
What do the Stone Crows do?</font>

285
00:21:35,410 --> 00:21:37,644
<font color="#FFFFFF">还不是只敢躲在石头后面发抖
Hide behind rocks and shiver</font>

286
00:21:37,679 --> 00:21:40,647
<font color="#FFFFFF">当谷地的骑士经过的时候?
when the knights of the Vale ride by?</font>

287
00:21:40,682 --> 00:21:43,317
<font color="#FFFFFF">你们就只偷得到这种货色?
Are those the best weapons you could steal?</font>

288
00:21:44,619 --> 00:21:46,554
<font color="#FFFFFF">杀羊或许可以,
Good enough for killing sheep,</font>

289
00:21:46,587 --> 00:21:48,322
<font color="#FFFFFF">还得那羊乖乖认命让你们杀.
if the sheep don't fight back.</font>

290
00:21:48,356 --> 00:21:50,557
<font color="#FFFFFF">兰尼斯特家的铁匠拉出的屎都比这高级.
Lannister smiths shit better steel.</font>

291
00:21:56,230 --> 00:21:59,633
<font color="#FFFFFF">你以为你能用你的小零碎换你的命?
You think you can win us over with your trinkets?</font>

292
00:22:10,511 --> 00:22:13,914
<font color="#FFFFFF">这小零碎比你们部落的所有东西都更值钱.
That trinket is worth more than everything your tribe owns.</font>

293
00:22:15,818 --> 00:22:19,189
<font color="#FFFFFF">如果你肯帮我们, 多夫之子夏嘎,
But if you help us, Shagga Son of Dolf,</font>

294
00:22:19,222 --> 00:22:21,892
<font color="#FFFFFF">我不止会给你小零碎.
I will not give you trinkets.</font>

295
00:22:21,925 --> 00:22:24,394
<font color="#FFFFFF">我会给你这个.
I will give you this.</font>

296
00:22:25,297 --> 00:22:26,897
<font color="#FFFFFF">什么 "这个"?
What is "this"?</font>

297
00:22:28,099 --> 00:22:30,601
<font color="#FFFFFF">整个艾林谷.
The Vale of Arryn.</font>

298
00:22:30,635 --> 00:22:33,938
<font color="#FFFFFF">艾林谷的领主们一直在欺压山地部落.
The Lords of the Vale have always spat upon the hill tribes.</font>

299
00:22:35,007 --> 00:22:38,175
<font color="#FFFFFF">艾林谷的领主们想要我死.
The Lords of the Vale want me dead.</font>

300
00:22:39,877 --> 00:22:42,980
<font color="#FFFFFF">我想是时候让谷地换一批新领主了.
I believe it is time for new Lords of the Vale.</font>

301
00:22:50,421 --> 00:22:52,721
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>真是难得一见的人物...
Ser Alliser: Now there's a rare sight—</i></font>

302
00:22:52,757 --> 00:22:56,259
<font color="#FFFFFF">不但是个野种, 还是个叛国者的野种呢.
not only a bastard, but a traitor's bastard.</font>

303
00:23:07,203 --> 00:23:10,006
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 琼恩, 不要! - 琼恩, 住手, 把刀放下!
- Jon, no! - Jon, stop, put it down!</font>

304
00:23:13,276 --> 00:23:15,344
<font color="#FFFFFF">血统决定善恶.
Blood will always tell.</font>

305
00:23:15,377 --> 00:23:18,515
<font color="#FFFFFF">你会被吊死的, 野种.
You'll hang for this, bastard.</font>

306
00:23:37,800 --> 00:23:41,035
<font color="#FFFFFF">我告诉过你别做傻事.
I told you not to do anything stupid.</font>

307
00:23:41,069 --> 00:23:44,704
<font color="#FFFFFF">你被关禁闭了. 去吧.
You're confined to quarters. Go.</font>

308
00:24:09,465 --> 00:24:11,400
<font color="#FFFFFF">白灵, 怎么了?
Ghost, what's wrong?</font>

309
00:24:12,536 --> 00:24:14,637
<font color="#FFFFFF">外面出什么事了?
Is something out there?</font>

310
00:24:46,502 --> 00:24:48,770
<font color="#FFFFFF">总司令?
Commander?</font>

311
00:24:52,009 --> 00:24:54,810
<font color="#FFFFFF">待在这里.
Stay.</font>

312
00:25:06,124 --> 00:25:08,358
<font color="#FFFFFF">喂?
Hello?</font>

313
00:25:17,269 --> 00:25:18,303
<font color="#FFFFFF">是谁?
Who's there?</font>

314
00:25:25,111 --> 00:25:28,046
<font color="#FFFFFF">总司令大人?
- Lord Commander? -</font>

315
00:25:54,541 --> 00:25:56,375
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>雪诺?
Snow?</i></font>

316
00:25:56,411 --> 00:25:58,010
<font color="#FFFFFF">总司令!
Commander!</font>

317
00:26:12,292 --> 00:26:13,925
<font color="#FFFFFF">快走, 快走!
Move move!</font>

318
00:26:32,546 --> 00:26:35,013
<font color="#FFFFFF">他们在干什么?
What did they do?</font>

319
00:26:51,099 --> 00:26:54,469
<font color="#FFFFFF">我以为多斯拉克人不信赖金钱.
I thought the Dothraki didn't believe in money.</font>

320
00:26:54,502 --> 00:26:58,405
<font color="#FFFFFF">金钱可以雇船, 公主,
Gold to hire ships, Princess,</font>

321
00:26:58,440 --> 00:27:01,276
<font color="#FFFFFF">乘船才能去维斯特洛.
ships to sail to Westeros.</font>

322
00:27:17,058 --> 00:27:19,527
<font color="#FFFFFF">乔拉, 叫他们住手.
Jorah, make them stop.</font>

323
00:27:19,560 --> 00:27:21,795
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 卡丽熙? - 你听到我的命令了.
- Khaleesi? - You heard me.</font>

324
00:27:21,829 --> 00:27:25,332
<font color="#FFFFFF">这些人为卡奥流血卖命, 如今该他们取得奖赏了.
These men have shed blood for their Khal. Now they claim their rewards.</font>

325
00:27:36,179 --> 00:27:38,547
<font color="#FFFFFF">公主, 你的心肠很软,
Princess, you have a gentle heart,</font>

326
00:27:38,580 --> 00:27:40,583
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>但战争就是这个样子.
but this is how it's always been.</i></font>

327
00:27:40,616 --> 00:27:43,586
<font color="#FFFFFF">我的心肠并不软, 爵士.
I do not have a gentle heart, Ser.</font>

328
00:27:55,999 --> 00:27:58,500
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>(吾血之血. 她是我的!)
Kash qoy qoyi thira disse. Me qorasokh anni!</i></font>

329
00:27:58,534 --> 00:28:02,670
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>- 来吧. - (她是我抓到的!)
Anha afichak mae m'arakhoon!</i></font>

330
00:28:07,909 --> 00:28:09,777
<font color="#FFFFFF">你要怎么处置她?
What do you want done with them?</font>

331
00:28:09,811 --> 00:28:12,378
<font color="#FFFFFF">把她带到我这儿来. 还有那些女人.
Bring her to me. And those women there.</font>

332
00:28:14,249 --> 00:28:16,682
<font color="#FFFFFF">您没法把她们全都收为己有, 公主.
You cannot claim them all, Princess.</font>

333
00:28:16,717 --> 00:28:18,751
<font color="#FFFFFF">我能,
I can,</font>

334
00:28:18,786 --> 00:28:21,488
<font color="#FFFFFF">我就要这样做.
and I will.</font>

335
00:28:21,522 --> 00:28:23,490
<font color="#FFFFFF">(操!)
Me Fati!</font>

336
00:28:23,523 --> 00:28:26,993
<font color="#FFFFFF">(卡丽熙抢了我的战利品,)
Khaleesi vazha anhaan qorasokh anni,</font>

337
00:28:27,028 --> 00:28:29,363
<font color="#FFFFFF">(本该是让我骑的羊女!)
ch'anha afichak mae m'arakhoon anni!</font>

338
00:28:29,396 --> 00:28:32,232
<font color="#FFFFFF">(等我见到她,)
Me vastoe hatif anni;</font>

339
00:28:32,267 --> 00:28:34,969
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>(我会问一下这件事.)
ahhazaan yer Nemo vacchaki.</i></font>

340
00:30:01,021 --> 00:30:03,923
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>(奥霍斯.)
Ohos.</i></font>

341
00:30:05,226 --> 00:30:07,093
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>(让开.)
Os.</i></font>

342
00:31:34,710 --> 00:31:36,845
<font color="#FFFFFF">谢谢您, 银发夫人.
Thank you, silver lady.</font>

343
00:31:39,082 --> 00:31:41,548
<font color="#FFFFFF">你是谁?
Who are you?</font>

344
00:31:41,584 --> 00:31:44,519
<font color="#FFFFFF">我叫弥丽马兹笃尔. 是这座神庙的女祭司.
I am named Mirri Maz Duur. I was the Godswife of this Temple.</font>

345
00:31:46,188 --> 00:31:48,923
<font color="#FFFFFF">我母亲是从前的女祭司.
My mother was Godswife here before me.</font>

346
00:31:48,958 --> 00:31:51,393
<font color="#FFFFFF">她教会我如何调制圣烟和圣膏.
She taught me how to make healing smokes and ointments.</font>

347
00:31:51,426 --> 00:31:54,430
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>所有人类都是同一群羔羊, 这是我们的信仰.
All men are of one flock, so my people believe.</i></font>

348
00:31:54,464 --> 00:31:56,566
<font color="#FFFFFF">至高牧神派我到世上医治他的...
The Great Shepherd sent me to Earth to heal his—</font>

349
00:32:02,207 --> 00:32:04,208
<font color="#FFFFFF">不论是羔羊或是狮子,
lamb or lion,</font>

350
00:32:04,241 --> 00:32:06,911
<font color="#FFFFFF">他的伤口必须立刻清洗缝针
his wound must be washed and sewn</font>

351
00:32:06,944 --> 00:32:09,211
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>不然会化脓的.
or it will fester.</i></font>

352
00:32:37,807 --> 00:32:41,109
<font color="#FFFFFF">三十年来我杀死过...
For 30 years I've been making corpses</font>

353
00:32:41,144 --> 00:32:42,978
<font color="#FFFFFF">无数敌人, 小子.
out of men, boy.</font>

354
00:32:43,012 --> 00:32:45,747
<font color="#FFFFFF">我最适合率领前锋.
I'm the man you want leading the Vanguard.</font>

355
00:32:47,115 --> 00:32:49,282
<font color="#FFFFFF">盖伯特葛洛佛才该率领前锋.
Galbart Glover will lead the Van.</font>

356
00:32:49,317 --> 00:32:51,984
<font color="#FFFFFF">除非他妈的长城整个融化
The bloody Wall will melt</font>

357
00:32:52,019 --> 00:32:55,087
<font color="#FFFFFF">否则安伯家别想走在葛洛佛家前头.
before an Umber marches behind a Glover.</font>

358
00:32:55,923 --> 00:32:58,157
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>我要率领前锋
I will lead the Van</i></font>

359
00:32:58,192 --> 00:33:00,492
<font color="#FFFFFF">否则我就带着我的人马
or I will take my men</font>

360
00:33:00,527 --> 00:33:02,627
<font color="#FFFFFF">班师回家.
and march them home.</font>

361
00:33:07,567 --> 00:33:10,236
<font color="#FFFFFF">欢迎你这么做, 安伯大人.
You are welcome to do so, Lord Umber.</font>

362
00:33:10,270 --> 00:33:13,339
<font color="#FFFFFF">等我收拾完兰尼斯特家
And when I am done with the Lannisters</font>

363
00:33:13,374 --> 00:33:15,674
<font color="#FFFFFF">我会立刻回师北上,
I will march back North,</font>

364
00:33:15,710 --> 00:33:17,176
<font color="#FFFFFF">把你从你的城堡里抓出来
root you out of your Keep</font>

365
00:33:17,211 --> 00:33:19,881
<font color="#FFFFFF">并当成背誓者吊死.
and hang you for an oathbreaker.</font>

366
00:33:19,914 --> 00:33:21,915
<font color="#FFFFFF">背誓者, 是吗?
Oathbreaker, is it?</font>

367
00:33:23,484 --> 00:33:26,054
<font color="#FFFFFF">我可不会干坐着任人侮辱
I'll not sit here and swallow insults</font>

368
00:33:26,087 --> 00:33:28,623
<font color="#FFFFFF">特别是象你这种刚从泥里钻出来的小鬼, 八成连尿都还有青草气.
from a boy so green he pisses grass.</font>

369
00:33:42,804 --> 00:33:45,105
<font color="#FFFFFF">我父亲曾教导我必须以死刑惩戒...
My Lord father taught me it was death to bare steel</font>

370
00:33:45,138 --> 00:33:47,207
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>敢对主君拔剑的封臣.
- against your Liege Lord. -</i></font>

371
00:33:47,240 --> 00:33:51,545
<font color="#FFFFFF">但我相信大琼恩只是想帮我切肉罢了.
But doubtless the Greatjon only meant to cut my meat for me.</font>

372
00:33:53,582 --> 00:33:56,017
<font color="#FFFFFF">你的肉...
Your meat...</font>

373
00:34:01,156 --> 00:34:03,826
<font color="#FFFFFF">还真他妈的硬.
is bloody tough.</font>

374
00:34:34,460 --> 00:34:37,429
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 怎么了? 出什么事了? - 嘘, 没什么.
- What is it? What's happened? - Shh, it's all right.</font>

375
00:34:41,902 --> 00:34:45,471
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 你要去哪儿? - 去南方. 去救父亲.
- Where are you going? - South. For father.</font>

376
00:34:45,505 --> 00:34:47,206
<font color="#FFFFFF">可现在是午夜啊.
But it's the middle of the night.</font>

377
00:34:47,240 --> 00:34:49,375
<font color="#FFFFFF">兰尼斯特家的探子无处不在.
The Lannisters have spies everywhere.</font>

378
00:34:49,409 --> 00:34:51,976
<font color="#FFFFFF">我不希望让他们知道我们已经出发.
I don't want them to know we're coming.</font>

379
00:34:52,012 --> 00:34:54,713
<font color="#FFFFFF">他们的人马比我们多.
They have more men than we do.</font>

380
00:34:54,748 --> 00:34:56,949
<font color="#FFFFFF">嗯, 是这样的.
Aye, they do.</font>

381
00:34:56,983 --> 00:34:59,050
<font color="#FFFFFF">我能和你一起去吗?
Can't I come with you?</font>

382
00:34:59,085 --> 00:35:01,586
<font color="#FFFFFF">现在我能骑马了. 你看过我骑马了.
I can ride now. You've seen me riding.</font>

383
00:35:01,621 --> 00:35:03,722
<font color="#FFFFFF">我不会再惹麻烦的, 我...
And I won't get in the way, I—</font>

384
00:35:03,757 --> 00:35:06,291
<font color="#FFFFFF">临冬城必须有史塔克家的人坐镇.
There must always be a Stark at Winterfell.</font>

385
00:35:06,326 --> 00:35:08,460
<font color="#FFFFFF">在我回来之前你就是城主.
Until I return that will be you.</font>

386
00:35:10,931 --> 00:35:14,199
<font color="#FFFFFF">我们走后你绝不能离开城堡. 明白吗?
You are not to leave the castle walls while we are gone. Do you understand?</font>

387
00:35:16,838 --> 00:35:20,206
<font color="#FFFFFF">好好听从鲁温师傅的教导. 好好照顾你的弟弟.
Listen to Maester Luwin. Look after your little brother.</font>

388
00:35:20,242 --> 00:35:22,376
<font color="#FFFFFF">我会的.
I will.</font>

389
00:35:22,411 --> 00:35:24,478
<font color="#FFFFFF">我有时间就会写信回来,
I'll send letters whenever I can,</font>

390
00:35:24,512 --> 00:35:26,748
<font color="#FFFFFF">但如果你很久没收到我的信,
but if you don't hear from me,</font>

391
00:35:26,782 --> 00:35:28,684
<font color="#FFFFFF">也不要担心.
don't be scared.</font>

392
00:35:33,791 --> 00:35:35,992
<font color="#FFFFFF">我会回来的.
Until I return.</font>

393
00:35:56,215 --> 00:35:59,282
<font color="#FFFFFF">你躲在那儿多久了?
How long have you been hiding out there?</font>

394
00:35:59,318 --> 00:36:02,786
<font color="#FFFFFF">罗柏会找你道别.
Robb will be looking for you to say goodbye.</font>

395
00:36:04,123 --> 00:36:06,056
<font color="#FFFFFF">他们全都走了.
They've all gone away.</font>

396
00:36:06,092 --> 00:36:09,027
<font color="#FFFFFF">他们很快就会回来. 罗柏会救出父亲
They'll be back soon. Robb will free father</font>

397
00:36:09,061 --> 00:36:11,262
<font color="#FFFFFF">他们会和母亲一道回来.
and they'll come back with mother.</font>

398
00:36:12,931 --> 00:36:15,434
<font color="#FFFFFF">不, 他们不会.
No, they won't.</font>

399
00:36:20,106 --> 00:36:22,208
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>请你们务必看顾罗柏.
Please watch over Robb.</i></font>

400
00:36:22,242 --> 00:36:24,710
<font color="#FFFFFF">也请你们看顾临冬城所所有人马.
And watch over all the other men from Winterfell.</font>

401
00:36:24,744 --> 00:36:27,913
<font color="#FFFFFF">还有, 还有席恩.
And Theon too, I suppose.</font>

402
00:36:33,619 --> 00:36:36,387
<font color="#FFFFFF">你听见了吗, 孩子?
You hear them, boy?</font>

403
00:36:36,422 --> 00:36:39,023
<font color="#FFFFFF">旧神正在回答你.
The Old Gods are answering you.</font>

404
00:36:39,057 --> 00:36:40,958
<font color="#FFFFFF">你在这里做什么?
What are you doing here?</font>

405
00:36:40,992 --> 00:36:43,862
<font color="#FFFFFF">他们也是我的神.
They're my Gods too.</font>

406
00:36:45,364 --> 00:36:48,967
<font color="#FFFFFF">在长城之外, 他们是惟一的真神.
Beyond the Wall, they're the only Gods.</font>

407
00:36:50,336 --> 00:36:52,639
<font color="#FFFFFF">即便奴隶也可以祈祷.
Even slaves are allowed to pray.</font>

408
00:36:52,672 --> 00:36:55,041
<font color="#FFFFFF">你可不是奴隶.
You're not a slave.</font>

409
00:36:57,110 --> 00:37:00,079
<font color="#FFFFFF">嗯, 你的朋友确实曾经拿刀抵住我的喉咙.
Well, your friend did put a knife to my throat.</font>

410
00:37:01,215 --> 00:37:03,817
<font color="#FFFFFF">我不是在抱怨, 小领主,
I'm not complaining, Little Lord,</font>

411
00:37:03,851 --> 00:37:06,585
<font color="#FFFFFF">只是说出事实.
just telling truths.</font>

412
00:37:07,887 --> 00:37:10,690
<font color="#FFFFFF">你说听见神说话是什么意思?
What did you mean about hearing the Gods?</font>

413
00:37:10,724 --> 00:37:13,059
<font color="#FFFFFF">你向他们祈求,
You asked them,</font>

414
00:37:13,092 --> 00:37:14,726
<font color="#FFFFFF">而他们正在回答.
they're answering you.</font>

415
00:37:14,762 --> 00:37:17,731
<font color="#FFFFFF">嘘.
Shh.</font>

416
00:37:17,764 --> 00:37:19,431
<font color="#FFFFFF">竖起耳朵.
Open your ears.</font>

417
00:37:24,871 --> 00:37:27,106
<font color="#FFFFFF">不过是风声.
It's only the wind.</font>

418
00:37:27,141 --> 00:37:30,143
<font color="#FFFFFF">你以为这风是谁送来的?
Who do you think sends the wind</font>

419
00:37:30,177 --> 00:37:32,144
<font color="#FFFFFF">如果不是诸神的话?
if not the Gods?</font>

420
00:37:32,179 --> 00:37:33,880
<font color="#FFFFFF">他们能看到你, 孩子.
They see you, boy.</font>

421
00:37:33,914 --> 00:37:36,317
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>他们也能听到你说话.
They hear you.</i></font>

422
00:37:37,952 --> 00:37:40,789
<font color="#FFFFFF">在你哥哥要去的地方, 他们无法帮他.
Your brother will get no help from them where he's going.</font>

423
00:37:40,822 --> 00:37:43,625
<font color="#FFFFFF">旧神在南方没有力量.
The Old Gods have no power in the South.</font>

424
00:37:43,659 --> 00:37:47,329
<font color="#FFFFFF">那儿的鱼梁木早已被砍伐一空.
The Weirwoods there were all cut down a long time ago.</font>

425
00:37:47,364 --> 00:37:50,132
<font color="#FFFFFF">没有眼睛, 他们如何看顾你哥哥呢?
How can they watch when they have no eyes?</font>

426
00:37:53,170 --> 00:37:57,039
<font color="#FFFFFF">嗯, 真是个大块头.
Well, there's a big man.</font>

427
00:37:57,072 --> 00:38:00,242
<font color="#FFFFFF">我敢说他有巨人的血统.
He has giants' blood in him or I'm the Queen.</font>

428
00:38:00,275 --> 00:38:02,643
<font color="#FFFFFF">回去找你的衣服, 阿多.
Go back and find your clothes, Hodor.</font>

429
00:38:02,677 --> 00:38:04,512
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>去穿衣服吧.
— Go dress.</i></font>

430
00:38:04,547 --> 00:38:06,079
<font color="#FFFFFF">阿多.
Hodor.</font>

431
00:38:09,217 --> 00:38:11,418
<font color="#FFFFFF">长城之外真的有巨人吗?
Are there really giants beyond the Wall?</font>

432
00:38:12,788 --> 00:38:15,757
<font color="#FFFFFF">有巨人, 还有比巨人更可怕的生物.
Giants and worse than giants.</font>

433
00:38:15,791 --> 00:38:18,760
<font color="#FFFFFF">我跟你哥哥说过,
I tried telling your brother,</font>

434
00:38:18,793 --> 00:38:20,594
<font color="#FFFFFF">他走错方向了.
he's marching the wrong way.</font>

435
00:38:20,628 --> 00:38:24,132
<font color="#FFFFFF">所有的人马, 他们应该去北方, 孩子.
All these swords, they should be going North, boy.</font>

436
00:38:24,166 --> 00:38:26,333
<font color="#FFFFFF">北方, 不是南方!
North, not south!</font>

437
00:38:29,072 --> 00:38:31,472
<font color="#FFFFFF">寒风已然吹起.
The cold winds are rising.</font>

438
00:38:47,458 --> 00:38:49,793
<font color="#FFFFFF">他们被异鬼做了手脚.
They were touched by White Walkers.</font>

439
00:38:51,329 --> 00:38:53,297
<font color="#FFFFFF">所以他们才会回来.
That's why they came back.</font>

440
00:38:53,331 --> 00:38:56,199
<font color="#FFFFFF">所以他们的眼睛才会变成蓝色.
That's why their eyes turned blue.</font>

441
00:38:56,233 --> 00:38:59,369
<font color="#FFFFFF">只有火能阻止他们.
Only fire will stop them.</font>

442
00:39:01,306 --> 00:39:03,072
<font color="#FFFFFF">你怎么知道的?
How do you know that?</font>

443
00:39:03,108 --> 00:39:04,842
<font color="#FFFFFF">我从书上看到的...
I read about it in a book—</font>

444
00:39:04,876 --> 00:39:07,945
<font color="#FFFFFF">伊蒙师傅的图书馆里的一本非常古老的书.
a very old book in Maester Aemon's library.</font>

445
00:39:10,481 --> 00:39:12,615
<font color="#FFFFFF">那本书还说了些什么?
What else did the book say?</font>

446
00:39:12,650 --> 00:39:14,550
<font color="#FFFFFF">异鬼
The White Walkers</font>

447
00:39:14,585 --> 00:39:17,353
<font color="#FFFFFF">在冰层之下沉睡了数千年.
sleep beneath the ice for thousands of years.</font>

448
00:39:17,387 --> 00:39:19,923
<font color="#FFFFFF">当他们苏醒的时候...
And when they wake up—</font>

449
00:39:20,925 --> 00:39:24,762
<font color="#FFFFFF">当他们苏醒的时候会怎样?
And when they wake up, what?</font>

450
00:39:27,731 --> 00:39:30,233
<font color="#FFFFFF">我希望长城足够高.
I hope The Wall is high enough.</font>

451
00:40:02,764 --> 00:40:05,065
<font color="#FFFFFF">是夏雪, 夫人.
Summer snows, My Lady.</font>

452
00:40:05,101 --> 00:40:08,135
<font color="#FFFFFF">罗柏马带来了北境的人马.
Robb's brought the North with him.</font>

453
00:40:14,344 --> 00:40:16,210
<font color="#FFFFFF">河间地的领主们正在败退
The River Lords are falling back</font>

454
00:40:16,246 --> 00:40:18,079
<font color="#FFFFFF">詹姆兰尼斯特在后面穷追不舍.
with Jaime Lannister at their heels.</font>

455
00:40:18,114 --> 00:40:21,516
<font color="#FFFFFF">而泰温大人正带着另一支兰尼斯特军队从南方进逼.
And Lord Tywin is bringing around a second Lannister army from the South.</font>

456
00:40:21,552 --> 00:40:24,320
<font color="#FFFFFF">我们的斥候报告说其规模比弑君者的更庞大.
Our scouts confirm it's even larger than the Kingslayer's.</font>

457
00:40:24,355 --> 00:40:27,625
<font color="#FFFFFF">管他一支还是两支军队, 北境之王...
One army or two, the Kings in the North</font>

458
00:40:27,659 --> 00:40:31,461
<font color="#FFFFFF">能够打垮十倍优势的敌人.
threw back hosts 10 times as large.</font>

459
00:40:34,965 --> 00:40:36,632
<font color="#FFFFFF">母亲!
Mother!</font>

460
00:40:40,038 --> 00:40:42,271
<font color="#FFFFFF">你气色很好.
You look well.</font>

461
00:40:43,773 --> 00:40:47,543
<font color="#FFFFFF">凯特琳夫人, 在此动乱时刻见到您真是高兴.
Lady Catelyn, you're a welcome sight in these troubled times.</font>

462
00:40:47,577 --> 00:40:50,045
<font color="#FFFFFF">我们没想到会在这里见到您, 夫人.
We had not thought to meet you here, My Lady.</font>

463
00:40:51,014 --> 00:40:53,583
<font color="#FFFFFF">我也没想到会来这里.
I had not thought to be here.</font>

464
00:40:53,617 --> 00:40:55,684
<font color="#FFFFFF">我想单独和我儿子讲几句话.
I would speak with my son alone.</font>

465
00:40:55,719 --> 00:40:58,021
<font color="#FFFFFF">相信诸位大人能够理解.
I know you will forgive me, My Lords.</font>

466
00:40:58,056 --> 00:41:00,289
<font color="#FFFFFF">你们听见夫人说的话了! 快动身!
You heard her! Move your asses!</font>

467
00:41:00,324 --> 00:41:02,659
<font color="#FFFFFF">快点, 到外面去.
Come on, out.</font>

468
00:41:02,695 --> 00:41:05,329
<font color="#FFFFFF">你也是, 葛雷乔伊. 你他妈的耳聋了吗?
You too, Greyjoy. Are you bloody deaf?</font>

469
00:41:05,364 --> 00:41:07,266
<font color="#FFFFFF">不要担心, 夫人.
Have no fear, My Lady.</font>

470
00:41:07,300 --> 00:41:10,068
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>我们会拿剑拥穿泰温兰尼斯特的屁眼...
We'll shove our swords up Tywin Lannister's bunghole</i></font>

471
00:41:10,101 --> 00:41:12,871
<font color="#FFFFFF">然后打下红堡救出奈德.
and then it's on to the Red Keep to free Ned.</font>

472
00:41:12,905 --> 00:41:15,838
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 你这老鬼头, 罗德利克. - 大琼恩.
- You old devil, Rodrik. - Jon.</font>

473
00:41:15,873 --> 00:41:18,208
<font color="#FFFFFF">你的功夫还没荒废, 是吗?
You're not wasting away, are you?</font>

474
00:41:29,452 --> 00:41:32,288
<font color="#FFFFFF">我还清楚地记得你出生那天的样子...
I remember the day you came into this world</font>

475
00:41:32,322 --> 00:41:35,358
<font color="#FFFFFF">脸红红的, 大声哭闹.
red-faced and squalling.</font>

476
00:41:36,860 --> 00:41:39,528
<font color="#FFFFFF">现在我却看到你率领着一支大军上战场.
And now I find you leading a host to war.</font>

477
00:41:40,563 --> 00:41:42,965
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 没别人了. - 没别人?
- There was no one else. - No one?</font>

478
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:45,735
<font color="#FFFFFF">我刚才见到的那些人是谁?
Who were those men I saw here?</font>

479
00:41:45,769 --> 00:41:48,838
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 他们都不是史塔克. - 他们都身经百战.
- None of them are Starks. - All of them are seasoned in battle.</font>

480
00:41:48,873 --> 00:41:51,909
<font color="#FFFFFF">如果你想把我送回临冬城...
If you think you can send me back to Winterfell—</font>

481
00:41:51,943 --> 00:41:54,210
<font color="#FFFFFF">哦, 我真希望能这么做.
Oh, would that I could.</font>

482
00:41:57,282 --> 00:41:59,250
<font color="#FFFFFF">我收到了...
There was...</font>

483
00:41:59,284 --> 00:42:01,719
<font color="#FFFFFF">一封信.
a letter.</font>

484
00:42:04,155 --> 00:42:05,590
<font color="#FFFFFF">珊莎写来的.
From Sansa.</font>

485
00:42:06,559 --> 00:42:08,860
<font color="#FFFFFF">你的意思是王后写来的.
From the Queen, you mean.</font>

486
00:42:16,833 --> 00:42:19,936
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 上面没有提到艾莉亚. - 确实没有.
- There's no mention of Arya. - No.</font>

487
00:42:30,547 --> 00:42:32,880
<font color="#FFFFFF">你带来多少人?
How many men do you have?</font>

488
00:42:32,914 --> 00:42:35,317
<font color="#FFFFFF">一万八千.
18,000.</font>

489
00:42:35,351 --> 00:42:37,818
<font color="#FFFFFF">如果我去君临向乔佛里屈膝下跪...
If I go to King's Landing and bend my knee to Joffrey—</font>

490
00:42:37,853 --> 00:42:40,922
<font color="#FFFFFF">不, 那样你将永远无法离开.
you would never be allowed to leave. No.</font>

491
00:42:40,956 --> 00:42:43,724
<font color="#FFFFFF">我们最大的希望... 或者说惟一的希望...
Our best hope— our only hope—</font>

492
00:42:43,759 --> 00:42:47,061
<font color="#FFFFFF">便是你能在战场上击败对手.
is that you can defeat them in the field.</font>

493
00:42:47,096 --> 00:42:49,130
<font color="#FFFFFF">如果我战败?
And if I lose?</font>

494
00:42:49,164 --> 00:42:51,699
<font color="#FFFFFF">你知道坦格利安家孩子们的下场吗...
Do you know what happened to the Targaryen children</font>

495
00:42:51,733 --> 00:42:54,737
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 当君临城陷的时候? - 他们在睡梦中被屠杀.
- when the Mad King fell? - They were butchered in their sleep.</font>

496
00:42:54,771 --> 00:42:57,472
<font color="#FFFFFF">是泰温兰尼斯特下的命令.
On the orders of Tywin Lannister.</font>

497
00:42:57,507 --> 00:43:00,210
<font color="#FFFFFF">多年的时光并没有使他变仁慈一点.
And the years have not made him kinder.</font>

498
00:43:03,313 --> 00:43:05,483
<font color="#FFFFFF">如果你战败,
If you lose,</font>

499
00:43:05,516 --> 00:43:08,219
<font color="#FFFFFF">你的父亲会死,
your father dies,</font>

500
00:43:08,253 --> 00:43:09,786
<font color="#FFFFFF">你的妹妹们也会死,
your sisters die,</font>

501
00:43:09,820 --> 00:43:12,054
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>我们都会死.
we die.</i></font>

502
00:43:14,625 --> 00:43:16,659
<font color="#FFFFFF">好吧, 那事情就简单了.
Well, that makes it simple then.</font>

503
00:43:17,994 --> 00:43:19,994
<font color="#FFFFFF">我想是这样.
I suppose it does.</font>

504
00:43:43,016 --> 00:43:46,251
<font color="#FFFFFF">现在最好由波隆和我两个过去.
From here it might be best if Bronn and I continue alone.</font>

505
00:43:46,286 --> 00:43:48,856
<font color="#FFFFFF">对泰温之子提利昂来说最好.
Best for Tyrion son of Tywin.</font>

506
00:43:48,889 --> 00:43:50,891
<font color="#FFFFFF">对我们来说可不好.
Not best for me.</font>

507
00:43:50,925 --> 00:43:54,094
<font color="#FFFFFF">如果半人背叛我们,
If the half man betrays us,</font>

508
00:43:54,128 --> 00:43:57,565
<font color="#FFFFFF">多夫之子夏嘎就会剁掉他的命根子...
Shagga Son of Dolf will cut off his manhood—</font>

509
00:43:57,599 --> 00:44:00,135
<font color="#FFFFFF">拿去喂山羊, 我知道.
and feed it to the goats, yes.</font>

510
00:44:02,639 --> 00:44:05,206
<font color="#FFFFFF">那好吧.
All right then.</font>

511
00:44:05,240 --> 00:44:07,443
<font color="#FFFFFF">我要去见我父亲了.
Time to meet my father.</font>

512
00:44:39,775 --> 00:44:42,577
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 提利昂. - 叔叔.
- Tyrion. - Uncle.</font>

513
00:44:42,612 --> 00:44:44,480
<font color="#FFFFFF">父亲.
Father.</font>

514
00:44:45,983 --> 00:44:48,983
<font color="#FFFFFF">看来关于你已死的传言不攻自破了.
The rumors of your demise were unfounded.</font>

515
00:44:49,018 --> 00:44:52,420
<font color="#FFFFFF">真抱歉让您失望了.
Sorry to disappoint you.</font>

516
00:44:52,454 --> 00:44:54,989
<font color="#FFFFFF">这些是什么人...
And who are these...</font>

517
00:44:55,023 --> 00:44:57,257
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>你的同伴?
Companions of yours?</i></font>

518
00:44:59,327 --> 00:45:01,760
<font color="#FFFFFF">这位是多夫之子夏嘎,
This is Shagga Son of Dolf,</font>

519
00:45:01,795 --> 00:45:04,164
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>石鸦部的酋长.
Chieftain of the Stone Crows.</i></font>

520
00:45:04,197 --> 00:45:08,568
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>提魅之子提魅, 灼人部的首领.
Timett Son of Timett, ruler of the Burned Men.</i></font>

521
00:45:08,601 --> 00:45:13,340
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>这位美少女是齐克之女齐拉
This fair maid is Chella daughter of Cheyk,</i></font>

522
00:45:13,373 --> 00:45:15,742
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>黑耳部的领袖.
leader of the Black Ears.</i></font>

523
00:45:15,777 --> 00:45:19,146
<font color="#FFFFFF">而这位是波隆, 谁人之子来着...
And here we have Bronn son of...</font>

524
00:45:19,181 --> 00:45:21,782
<font color="#FFFFFF">你不会认识他的.
You wouldn't know him.</font>

525
00:45:23,786 --> 00:45:26,355
<font color="#FFFFFF">可否允许我为各位介绍我的父亲大人,
May I present My Lord Father,</font>

526
00:45:26,389 --> 00:45:29,023
<font color="#FFFFFF">兰尼斯特家族的泰陀斯之子泰温,
Tywin son of Tytos of House Lannister,</font>

527
00:45:29,059 --> 00:45:32,126
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>凯岩城主暨西境守护.
Lord of Casterly Rock and Warden of the West?</i></font>

528
00:45:34,097 --> 00:45:36,733
<font color="#FFFFFF">非常感谢您为我出兵打仗.
Kind of you to go to war for me.</font>

529
00:45:39,769 --> 00:45:41,704
<font color="#FFFFFF">你使我们别无选择.
You left us no choice.</font>

530
00:45:41,739 --> 00:45:43,806
<font color="#FFFFFF">这事关家族的荣誉.
The honor of the House was at stake.</font>

531
00:45:45,309 --> 00:45:48,478
<font color="#FFFFFF">你哥哥詹姆绝不会如此轻易地束手就擒的.
Your brother would never have submitted to capture so meekly.</font>

532
00:45:48,512 --> 00:45:51,047
<font color="#FFFFFF">我们确实有所不同, 詹姆和我.
We have our differences, Jaime and I.</font>

533
00:45:51,081 --> 00:45:53,250
<font color="#FFFFFF">他更勇敢. 而我更帅气.
He's braver. I'm better looking.</font>

534
00:45:53,284 --> 00:45:55,619
<font color="#FFFFFF">他满身都是荣耀.
He's been covering himself in glory.</font>

535
00:45:55,653 --> 00:45:58,889
<font color="#FFFFFF">詹姆在金牙城外击溃了三河诸侯,
Jaime smashed the River Lords at the Golden Tooth,</font>

536
00:45:58,923 --> 00:46:02,592
<font color="#FFFFFF">现在正在围攻奔流城, 凯特琳史塔克的老家.
and now lays siege to Riverrun, Catelyn Stark's homeland.</font>

537
00:46:02,626 --> 00:46:04,728
<font color="#FFFFFF">史塔克家在做什么? 艾德大人?
And the Starks? Lord Eddard?</font>

538
00:46:04,762 --> 00:46:08,831
<font color="#FFFFFF">—现在是我们的人质. 他在地牢里无法带兵打仗.
—Is our hostage. He will lead no armies from his dungeon cell.</font>

539
00:46:08,867 --> 00:46:10,900
<font color="#FFFFFF">我那美丽的姐姐是怎么说服国王
How did my sweet sister persuade the King</font>

540
00:46:10,934 --> 00:46:12,802
<font color="#FFFFFF">囚禁他亲爱的朋友奈德的?
to imprison his dear friend Ned?</font>

541
00:46:12,838 --> 00:46:16,807
<font color="#FFFFFF">劳勃拜拉席恩死了. 如今是乔佛里在君临执政.
Robert Baratheon is dead. Joffrey rules in King's Landing.</font>

542
00:46:19,813 --> 00:46:21,780
<font color="#FFFFFF">你的意思是说是我姐姐在执政.
My sister rules, you mean.</font>

543
00:46:22,983 --> 00:46:25,284
<font color="#FFFFFF">史塔克的儿子已经下令召集封臣.
Stark's son has called his banners.</font>

544
00:46:25,318 --> 00:46:28,755
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 他正带着一支大军南下. - 不过是个毛头小子.
- He moves south with a strong host. - A green boy.</font>

545
00:46:28,789 --> 00:46:30,556
<font color="#FFFFFF">等他尝到战斗的滋味就会...
One taste of battle and he'll run</font>

546
00:46:30,590 --> 00:46:33,159
<font color="#FFFFFF">夹着尾巴逃回临冬城.
back to Winterfell wi his tail between his legs.</font>

547
00:46:34,362 --> 00:46:35,862
<font color="#FFFFFF">也许吧.
Maybe.</font>

548
00:46:35,896 --> 00:46:38,465
<font color="#FFFFFF">不过那小子确实很好战.
Though the boy does have a certain belligerence.</font>

549
00:46:38,498 --> 00:46:41,001
<font color="#FFFFFF">你会喜欢他的.
You'd like him.</font>

550
00:46:41,034 --> 00:46:45,072
<font color="#FFFFFF">既然我们说到打仗的事情,
While we're on the subject of war,</font>

551
00:46:45,106 --> 00:46:47,807
<font color="#FFFFFF">我对这几位朋友做过承诺
I made promises to my friends here</font>

552
00:46:47,842 --> 00:46:50,210
<font color="#FFFFFF">而兰尼斯特有债必还.
and a Lannister always pays his debts.</font>

553
00:46:50,244 --> 00:46:53,313
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>我们需要三千个头盔和盾牌,
We shall require 3,000 helms and shields,</i></font>

554
00:46:53,347 --> 00:46:55,581
<font color="#FFFFFF">还有刀剑, 长枪,
plus swords, pikes,</font>

555
00:46:55,615 --> 00:46:57,416
<font color="#FFFFFF">护甲, 钉锤...
gorgets, maces—</font>

556
00:46:57,451 --> 00:47:00,018
<font color="#FFFFFF">如果大人同意,
if it please My Lord,</font>

557
00:47:00,052 --> 00:47:02,121
<font color="#FFFFFF">亚当爵士要我来报告, 北境军队
Ser Addam bids me report that the Northmen</font>

558
00:47:02,155 --> 00:47:03,554
<font color="#FFFFFF">已经越过了颈泽.
have crossed the neck.</font>

559
00:47:05,557 --> 00:47:08,025
<font color="#FFFFFF">小狼就要钻进狮口了.
The wolf rushes into the lion's jaws.</font>

560
00:47:08,059 --> 00:47:12,297
<font color="#FFFFFF">好吧. 凯冯, 立刻下令敲鼓集合.
So be it. Kevan, command the drummers beat assembly.</font>

561
00:47:13,800 --> 00:47:16,936
<font color="#FFFFFF">并送信给詹姆说我将前去同罗柏史塔克决战.
And send word to Jaime that I am moving against Robb Stark.</font>

562
00:47:16,969 --> 00:47:18,938
<font color="#FFFFFF">遵命, 大人.
At once, My Lord.</font>

563
00:47:31,887 --> 00:47:34,855
<font color="#FFFFFF">听说山地部落的人都是伟大的战士.
It is said that the men of the Mountain clans are great warriors.</font>

564
00:47:34,889 --> 00:47:36,623
<font color="#FFFFFF">与我一同出兵作战
Ride with me against my enemies</font>

565
00:47:36,657 --> 00:47:39,693
<font color="#FFFFFF">你们将得到我儿子承诺的一切, 甚至更多.
and you shall have all my son promised you and more.</font>

566
00:47:39,728 --> 00:47:41,963
<font color="#FFFFFF">但这个半人得跟我们一起作战.
Only if the half man fights with us.</font>

567
00:47:41,998 --> 00:47:45,434
<font color="#FFFFFF">直到我们拿到他答应的武器,
Until we hold the steel he pledged us,</font>

568
00:47:45,469 --> 00:47:47,869
<font color="#FFFFFF">这小狮子的命是我们的.
the little lion's life is ours.</font>

569
00:47:53,443 --> 00:47:56,112
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>斥候报告说泰温大人正在北上.
The scouts report Lord Tywin moves north.</i></font>

570
00:47:56,146 --> 00:47:57,980
<font color="#FFFFFF">我们需要凭借险要地形截住他,
We need to get him on broken ground,</font>

571
00:47:58,014 --> 00:47:59,681
<font color="#FFFFFF">使他的骑士无法发挥力量.
put his Knights at a disadvantage.</font>

572
00:47:59,715 --> 00:48:01,818
<font color="#FFFFFF">不, 我们要从他侧面绕过去
No, we need to get around him</font>

573
00:48:01,851 --> 00:48:04,753
<font color="#FFFFFF">并打破詹姆兰尼斯特对奔流城的围攻.
and break Jaime Lannister's siege of Riverrun.</font>

574
00:48:04,789 --> 00:48:07,623
<font color="#FFFFFF">这样三河诸候就会加入我们的队伍.
Do that and the River Lords will join us.</font>

575
00:48:07,657 --> 00:48:09,525
<font color="#FFFFFF">无论怎样做我们都需要先过绿叉河
To do either we need to cross the river</font>

576
00:48:09,559 --> 00:48:11,226
<font color="#FFFFFF">而孪河城是过河的惟一路线.
and the only crossing is at The Twins.</font>

577
00:48:11,260 --> 00:48:13,295
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>佛雷大人控制着孪河桥.
Lord Frey controls that bridge.</i></font>

578
00:48:13,329 --> 00:48:14,896
<font color="#FFFFFF">他是你父亲的封臣.
Your father's bannerman.</font>

579
00:48:14,931 --> 00:48:18,166
<font color="#FFFFFF">我父亲称他为 "迟到的佛雷大人"
"The late Lord Frey" my father calls him.</font>

580
00:48:18,201 --> 00:48:21,704
<font color="#FFFFFF">当年三叉戟河之战, 他在战斗结束后才现身.
At the Trident, he didn't appear until the battle was done.</font>

581
00:48:21,737 --> 00:48:25,775
<font color="#FFFFFF">不是每个人都把自己的誓言当回事的.
Some men takes their oaths more seriously than others.</font>

582
00:48:33,182 --> 00:48:35,918
<font color="#FFFFFF">罗柏说得对. 我们需要那座桥.
Robb's right. We need that bridge.</font>

583
00:48:35,952 --> 00:48:38,052
<font color="#FFFFFF">那么该怎么办?
So what's it going to be?</font>

584
00:48:38,088 --> 00:48:41,489
<font color="#FFFFFF">我们先对付詹姆还是泰温?
Do we move against Jaime or Lord Tywin?</font>

585
00:48:45,661 --> 00:48:47,195
<font color="#FFFFFF">打扰了, 大人.
Your pardon, my lords.</font>

586
00:48:47,230 --> 00:48:49,898
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>我们抓住了一个兰尼斯特军的斥候.
We've captured a Lannister scout.</i></font>

587
00:48:51,802 --> 00:48:55,137
<font color="#FFFFFF">别担心, 小伙子. 他不会活着离开这个帐篷.
Don't worry, lad. He won't b leaving this tent with his head.</font>

588
00:48:56,474 --> 00:48:58,141
<font color="#FFFFFF">你们在哪儿发现他的?
Where did you find him?</font>

589
00:48:58,175 --> 00:49:00,309
<font color="#FFFFFF">在营地周围的树丛里.
In the brush above the encampment.</font>

590
00:49:00,344 --> 00:49:02,211
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>他好象正在估算人数.
He looked to be counting.</i></font>

591
00:49:12,657 --> 00:49:14,458
<font color="#FFFFFF">你算出来有多少人?
How high did you get?</font>

592
00:49:16,827 --> 00:49:18,829
<font color="#FFFFFF">两万. 或许更多.
20,000. Maybe more.</font>

593
00:49:19,864 --> 00:49:21,597
<font color="#FFFFFF">你不必自己动手行刑.
You don't have to do this yourself.</font>

594
00:49:21,632 --> 00:49:23,199
<font color="#FFFFFF">您父亲会理解的...
Your father would understand—</font>

595
00:49:23,233 --> 00:49:27,269
<font color="#FFFFFF">我父亲懂得仁慈, 如果不是非杀不可.
My father unrstands mercy, when there is room for it.</font>

596
00:49:28,672 --> 00:49:30,505
<font color="#FFFFFF">他也懂得荣誉...
And he understands honor...</font>

597
00:49:33,311 --> 00:49:35,577
<font color="#FFFFFF">和勇气.
and courage.</font>

598
00:49:37,481 --> 00:49:39,315
<font color="#FFFFFF">放他走吧.
Let him go.</font>

599
00:49:40,284 --> 00:49:42,684
<font color="#FFFFFF">罗柏.
Robb.</font>

600
00:49:54,697 --> 00:49:57,664
<font color="#FFFFFF">去告诉泰温大人, 凛冬将至.
Tell Lord Tywin Winter is coming for him.</font>

601
00:49:57,699 --> 00:50:02,635
<font color="#FFFFFF">两万北境大军正在南下, 看看他是不是真的能拉金屎.
20,000 Northerners marching south to find out if he really does shit gold.</font>

602
00:50:04,706 --> 00:50:06,206
<font color="#FFFFFF">遵命, 大人.
Yes, My Lord.</font>

603
00:50:06,239 --> 00:50:08,041
<font color="#FFFFFF">多谢, 大人.
Thank you, My Lord.</font>

604
00:50:17,485 --> 00:50:21,188
<font color="#FFFFFF">你疯了吗, 孩子? 放他走?
Are you touched, boy? Letting him go?</font>

605
00:50:21,222 --> 00:50:23,257
<font color="#FFFFFF">你又称我孩子了.
You call me boy again.</font>

606
00:50:24,760 --> 00:50:26,393
<font color="#FFFFFF">下去吧.
Go on.</font>

607
00:50:43,409 --> 00:50:46,612
<font color="#FFFFFF">喂.
Oi.</font>

608
00:50:51,684 --> 00:50:54,353
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>国王陛下决定...
It is also the wish of His Grace</i></font>

609
00:50:54,387 --> 00:50:59,693
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>尽忠职守的杰诺斯史林特,
that his loyal servant Janos Slynt,</i></font>

610
00:50:59,726 --> 00:51:02,829
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>- 都城守卫队司令... - 艾伦爵士.
- Commander of the City Watch... - Ser Aron.</i></font>

611
00:51:02,864 --> 00:51:06,434
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>立刻擢升为贵族...
Be at once raised to the rank of Lord...</i></font>

612
00:51:06,467 --> 00:51:11,938
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>- 盖尔斯大人. - ... 赐予古老的赫伦堡,
- Lord Gyles. - ... And granted the ancient seat of Harrenhal,</i></font>

613
00:51:11,972 --> 00:51:15,809
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>其子嗣将世代继承此等荣耀
and that his sons and grandsons shall hold this honor</i></font>

614
00:51:15,842 --> 00:51:20,947
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>直到世界末日.
after him until the end of time.</i></font>

615
00:51:24,784 --> 00:51:28,119
<font color="#FFFFFF">为取代叛徒艾德史塔克,
In the place of the traitor Eddard Stark,</font>

616
00:51:28,153 --> 00:51:32,824
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>国王陛下决定由泰温兰尼斯特,
it is the wish of his Grace that Tywin Lannister,</i></font>

617
00:51:32,858 --> 00:51:36,661
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>凯岩城主暨西境守护,
Lord of Casterly Rock and Warden of the West,</i></font>

618
00:51:36,695 --> 00:51:40,798
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>担任国王之手.
be appointed Hand of the King.</i></font>

619
00:51:40,833 --> 00:51:42,733
<font color="#FFFFFF">最后,
Lastly,</font>

620
00:51:42,768 --> 00:51:45,603
<font color="#FFFFFF">于此密谋四起, 动乱不堪之际,
in these times of treason and turmoil,</font>

621
00:51:45,637 --> 00:51:48,873
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>御前会议认为...
it is the view of the Council</i></font>

622
00:51:48,907 --> 00:51:54,144
<font color="#FFFFFF">乔佛里国王的生命安全
that the life and safety</font>

623
00:51:51,476 --> 00:51:54,144
<font color="#FFFFFF">of King Joffrey</font>

624
00:51:54,179 --> 00:51:58,416
<font color="#FFFFFF">实乃第一要务.
be of paramount importance.</font>

625
00:52:00,018 --> 00:52:02,552
<font color="#FFFFFF">巴利斯坦赛尔弥爵士.
Ser Barristan Selmy.</font>

626
00:52:08,893 --> 00:52:12,396
<font color="#FFFFFF">陛下, 我听候您的差遣.
Your Grace, I am yours to command.</font>

627
00:52:12,431 --> 00:52:14,532
<font color="#FFFFFF">请起, 巴利斯坦爵士.
Rise, Ser Barristan.</font>

628
00:52:15,402 --> 00:52:17,503
<font color="#FFFFFF">你可以卸下头盔了.
You may remove your helm.</font>

629
00:52:22,443 --> 00:52:25,045
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>长久以来你为国效命，尽忠职守.
You have served the Realm long and faithfully.</i></font>

630
00:52:25,079 --> 00:52:29,050
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>七国上下每个人都对你心怀感激.
Every man and woman in the Seven Kingdoms owes you thanks.</i></font>

631
00:52:29,085 --> 00:52:32,353
<font color="#FFFFFF">然而是时候让你卸下你的铠甲和宝剑了.
But it is time to put aside your armor and your sword.</font>

632
00:52:32,387 --> 00:52:35,289
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>你该安享晚年, 并自豪地回顾...
It is time to rest and look back with pride</i></font>

633
00:52:35,324 --> 00:52:36,958
<font color="#FFFFFF">你长久以来的功绩了.
on your many years of service.</font>

634
00:52:39,161 --> 00:52:41,596
<font color="#FFFFFF">陛下, 御林铁卫乃是宣誓效命的兄弟.
Your Grace, the Kingsguard is a sworn brotherhood.</font>

635
00:52:41,630 --> 00:52:43,797
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>我们必须终身守誓.
Our vows are taken for life.</i></font>

636
00:52:43,833 --> 00:52:46,335
<font color="#FFFFFF">惟有一死才能解除我们的神圣使命.
Only death relieves us of our sacred trust.</font>

637
00:52:46,369 --> 00:52:50,072
<font color="#FFFFFF">是谁的死, 巴利斯坦爵士? 是你还是你的国王?
Whose death, Ser Barristan? Yours or your King's?</font>

638
00:52:50,106 --> 00:52:52,974
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>我父亲的死就是你的责任.
You let my father die.</i></font>

639
00:52:53,009 --> 00:52:55,945
<font color="#FFFFFF">你太老了, 谁都保护不了.
You're too old to protect anybody.</font>

640
00:52:58,248 --> 00:53:00,983
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 陛下— - 御前会议已经决定
- Your Grace— - The Council has determined</font>

641
00:53:01,018 --> 00:53:03,452
<font color="#FFFFFF">由詹姆兰尼斯特爵士接替你的职务
that Ser Jaime Lannister will take your place</font>

642
00:53:03,487 --> 00:53:05,755
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>担任御林铁卫队长.
as Lord Commander of the Kingsguard.</i></font>

643
00:53:05,789 --> 00:53:07,324
<font color="#FFFFFF">那个人玷污了自己的宝剑
The man who profaned his blade</font>

644
00:53:07,358 --> 00:53:09,559
<font color="#FFFFFF">杀死了他宣誓要保护的国王!
with the blood of the King he had sworn to defend!</font>

645
00:53:09,594 --> 00:53:11,527
<font color="#FFFFFF">小心一点, 爵士.
Careful, Ser.</font>

646
00:53:11,561 --> 00:53:13,262
<font color="#FFFFFF">我们并非不知感恩
We have nothing but gratitude</font>

647
00:53:13,297 --> 00:53:15,766
<font color="#FFFFFF">您的长期贡献有目共睹, 爵士.
for your long service, good Ser.</font>

648
00:53:15,800 --> 00:53:18,268
<font color="#FFFFFF">您将得到一座坚固的海滨城堡,
You shall be given a stout Keep beside the sea,</font>

649
00:53:18,302 --> 00:53:20,637
<font color="#FFFFFF">以及满足您需要的大批仆役.
with servants to look after your every need.</font>

650
00:53:20,670 --> 00:53:22,871
<font color="#FFFFFF">给我一个养老的地方
A hall to die in</font>

651
00:53:22,907 --> 00:53:25,307
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>以及为我送终的人.
and men to bury me.</i></font>

652
00:53:26,909 --> 00:53:29,945
<font color="#FFFFFF">我既生为一名骑士.
I am a Knight.</font>

653
00:53:29,980 --> 00:53:33,016
<font color="#FFFFFF">也要死得像个骑士.
I shall die a Knight.</font>

654
00:53:38,956 --> 00:53:41,090
<font color="#FFFFFF">像个没穿衣服的骑士, 是吧.
A naked Knight, apparently.</font>

655
00:53:52,235 --> 00:53:55,672
<font color="#FFFFFF">即便现在我仍可以像切蛋糕一样把你们五个通通砍倒!
Even now I could cut through the five of you like carving a cake!</font>

656
00:53:59,844 --> 00:54:02,378
<font color="#FFFFFF">拿去, 小子!
Here, boy!</font>

657
00:54:02,413 --> 00:54:04,847
<font color="#FFFFFF">把它熔了加到铁王座上吧.
Melt it down and add it to the others.</font>

658
00:54:21,364 --> 00:54:23,699
<font color="#FFFFFF">如果在场各位还有其他事...
If any man in this hall has other matters</font>

659
00:54:23,733 --> 00:54:26,867
<font color="#FFFFFF">请现在向国王陛下禀报
to set before His Grace, let him speak now</font>

660
00:54:26,902 --> 00:54:30,139
<font color="#FFFFFF">否则退朝.
or go forth and hold his silence.</font>

661
00:54:32,809 --> 00:54:34,945
<font color="#FFFFFF">陛下.
Your Grace.</font>

662
00:54:34,978 --> 00:54:37,347
<font color="#FFFFFF">请上前来, 小姐.
Come forward, My Lady.</font>

663
00:54:39,117 --> 00:54:41,853
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>史塔克家族的珊莎小姐.
The Lady Sansa of House Stark.</i></font>

664
00:54:43,389 --> 00:54:46,791
<font color="#FFFFFF">珊莎, 你有事禀报国王陛下和御前会议?
Do you have some business for the King and the Council, Sansa?</font>

665
00:54:46,826 --> 00:54:48,659
<font color="#FFFFFF">是的.
I do.</font>

666
00:54:53,532 --> 00:54:56,634
<font color="#FFFFFF">启禀陛下, 我要为我父亲请求您的慈悲,
As it please Your Grace, I ask mercy for my father,</font>

667
00:54:56,668 --> 00:55:00,137
<font color="#FFFFFF">艾德史塔克大人, 前任国王之手.
Lord Eddard Stark, who was Hand of the King.</font>

668
00:55:00,172 --> 00:55:03,039
<font color="#FFFFFF">叛国大罪好似带毒的野草.
Treason is a noxious weed.</font>

669
00:55:03,074 --> 00:55:07,244
<font color="#FFFFFF">- 必须连根拔除... - 让她说下去.
- It should be torn out, root— - Let her speak.</font>

670
00:55:07,280 --> 00:55:09,981
<font color="#FFFFFF">我要听听她的话.
I want to hear what she says.</font>

671
00:55:10,016 --> 00:55:12,150
<font color="#FFFFFF">感谢您, 陛下.
Thank you, Your Grace.</font>

672
00:55:12,184 --> 00:55:14,788
<font color="#FFFFFF">你要否认你父亲所犯罪行?
Do you deny your father's crime?</font>

673
00:55:14,822 --> 00:55:19,293
<font color="#FFFFFF">不, 诸位大人. 我明白他必须接受惩罚.
No, My Lords. I know he must be punished.</font>

674
00:55:19,327 --> 00:55:21,327
<font color="#FFFFFF">我请求的只是慈悲为怀.
All I ask is mercy.</font>

675
00:55:21,362 --> 00:55:24,231
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>我知道我父亲必定对其所为懊悔不已.
I know My Lord father must regret what he did.</i></font>

676
00:55:24,266 --> 00:55:26,568
<font color="#FFFFFF">他是劳勃国王的好友, 他敬爱国王.
He was King Robert's friend and he loved him.</font>

677
00:55:26,601 --> 00:55:28,802
<font color="#FFFFFF">你们知道他是真心敬爱他.
You all know he loved him.</font>

678
00:55:28,838 --> 00:55:32,440
<font color="#FFFFFF">他从未想当国王之手, 直到国王要求他.
He never wanted to be Hand until the King asked him.</font>

679
00:55:32,474 --> 00:55:35,876
<font color="#FFFFFF">他必定是受人蛊惑... 蓝礼大人或史坦尼斯大人
They must have lied to him— Lord Renly or Lord Stannis</font>

680
00:55:35,909 --> 00:55:38,711
<font color="#FFFFFF">或是其他什么人. 他们欺骗了他!
or somebody. They must have lied!</font>

681
00:55:38,746 --> 00:55:41,215
<font color="#FFFFFF">他说我不是国王.
He said I wasn't the King.</font>

682
00:55:41,248 --> 00:55:43,315
<font color="#FFFFFF">他为什么要那样说?
Why did he say that?</font>

683
00:55:43,351 --> 00:55:45,619
<font color="#FFFFFF">他受了重伤.
He was badly hurt.</font>

684
00:55:45,652 --> 00:55:48,521
<font color="#FFFFFF">派席尔大学士给他服用了罂粟花奶.
Maester Pycelle was giving him milk of the poppy.</font>

685
00:55:48,554 --> 00:55:52,724
<font color="#FFFFFF">当时他神智不清. 否则他绝不会那样说的.
He wasn't himself. Otherwise h never would have said it.</font>

686
00:55:55,061 --> 00:55:58,931
<font color="#FFFFFF">孩子对父亲的信赖... 多么单纯天真.
A child's faith... Such sweet innocence.</font>

687
00:55:58,965 --> 00:56:02,635
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>可是人们不是常说, 智慧之言往往来自
And yet they say wisdom oft comes</i></font>

688
00:56:02,670 --> 00:56:04,503
<font color="#FFFFFF">孩童之口么.
from the mouths of babes.</font>

689
00:56:04,538 --> 00:56:08,675
<font color="#FFFFFF">但叛国就是叛国!
Treason is treason!</font>

690
00:56:11,813 --> 00:56:13,980
<font color="#FFFFFF">你还有什么事?
Anything else?</font>

691
00:56:15,550 --> 00:56:18,952
<font color="#FFFFFF">如果您心里仍然有我,
If you still have any affection in your heart for me,</font>

692
00:56:18,985 --> 00:56:22,487
<font color="#FFFFFF">请成全我这个心愿吧, 陛下.
please do me this kindness, Your Grace.</font>

693
00:56:32,065 --> 00:56:34,331
<font color="#FFFFFF">你的肺腑之言感动了我.
Your sweet words have moved me.</font>

694
00:56:36,735 --> 00:56:39,302
<font color="#FFFFFF">但你父亲必须先俯首认罪.
But your father has to confess.</font>

695
00:56:39,338 --> 00:56:42,940
<font color="#FFFFFF">他必须承认我是他的国王...
He has to confess and say that I'm the King...</font>

696
00:56:45,842 --> 00:56:47,978
<font color="#FFFFFF">不然我无法手下留情.
Or there'll be no mercy for him.</font>

697
00:56:52,449 --> 00:56:54,550
<font color="#FFFFFF">他一定会的.
He will.</font>

698
00:57:04,586 --> 00:57:08,586
